Date: 1996-12-11

Title: Higher Dimensional SUSY Quantum Mechanics

Authors: Ashok Das, Sergio. A. Pernice

Comments: 8 pages, Latex

Journal-ref: Mod.Phys.Lett. A12 (1997) 581-588

Higher dimensional supersymmetric quantum mechanics is studied. Generalproperties of the two dimensional case are presented. For three spatialdimesions or higher, a spin structure is shown to arise naturally from thenonrelativistic supersymmetry algebra.